{"tid":1379251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（記住記住）放彈記住唔好掛住自己走！","createTime":"2019-07-28T18:17:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T02:17:53.000Z","uid":255497,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"39d607dde88c562ac8f041ddf9cc49bc186389fc","tid":1379251,"uid":255497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:17:02.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇番新聞<br />\n大街每次放蛋 人多既話就會有一堆人退 <br />\n一退後就塞死晒 跟手速龍一上前 <br />\n將塞死晒既人一拉拉向後 比後面班防暴處理 <br />\n再繼續抆人扯低 ！<br />\n所以好希望大家 有蛋哥陣真係要退既話 <br />\n唔撚該你地 捉實前面哥個 唔好比佢比速龍拉走<br />\n仲有好希望 有齊豬嘴先企前面啦好無<br />\n一放蛋你地無裝備既人又係咁往後退塞死晒<br />\n前線既人 屌你老母咩<br />\n<br />\n最後希望大家多點走入內街<br />\n唔好再係大街同班狗仔玩 大街玩唔著數<br />\n旺角哥次咁成功都係因為咁<br />\n班狗仔好驚入橫街窄巷"},{"pid":"a8e671e4aa8b1d77cedfd986511fe50ffe405e47","tid":1379251,"uid":255497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:17:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eed6b6dab9ec1f1a1482b28ac77ca30c37fa4880","tid":1379251,"uid":255497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:17:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e826fe890a3406aac2cc1d11af771bdfea7686b6","tid":1379251,"uid":255497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:18:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06158d1e4eaa77cf291e7d1c0d9d3f508fe7c09c","tid":1379251,"uid":255497,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:18:28.000Z","msg":"無裝備唔好上前 <br />\n有裝備既唔撚好怕死企後面啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"8bb395a96101725d70b77f5cbbeb596db2eae0ad","tid":1379251,"uid":265019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MYspSnv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMYspSnv.png&h=5134f868&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LuctzAR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLuctzAR.png&h=ca027caa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yOj0qHy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy